short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Removes cringe worthy comments from "StickMaster500" from all YouTube comment sections.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: When you load a YouTube video page, it waits until the comments section is loaded and then removes unwanted spam comments from the YouTube user "StickMaster500". No other comments are affected.
